{"tid":386400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要不要武力攻擊北韓 川普：我們等著瞧","createTime":"2017-09-03T23:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:47:22.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b10b0954f1820f4b4732e4858903ae96aa6314","tid":386400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:46:26.000Z","msg":"要不要武力攻擊北韓 川普：我們等著瞧 <br />\n<br />\n北韓昨（3日）進行核試爆，引發國際緊張。美國總統川普事後在推特說，南韓正發現對 北韓的「綏靖對談」根本沒用，北韓「只懂一個東西」，似乎暗示唯有動武才能讓北韓學 到教訓。 川普昨參加完教會的禮拜後，被記者問到是否將攻擊北韓，川普回答：「我們等著瞧。」（We&rsquo;ll see.）。北韓昨天的核試爆，是川普今年一月上台以來的首次核試爆 ，但已經是北韓歷來第六次的核試爆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/jBKkAS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjBKkAS&d=iWKpAqkzlq17HVprlYwAXkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=559e844c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/jBKkAS</a>"},{"pid":"64ba914bf367b5a7735d647a3ac718e508f0321a","tid":386400,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdd5d22eb42d3a49ef16090bdd4cb1bcbe32a13","tid":386400,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c86371d0710184c95d431ea2ef54fb7f16e276","tid":386400,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:34:49.000Z","msg":"鳩u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c564af1de11207053060d4048ecdd86e3ef45f5","tid":386400,"uid":38757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"特朗普上任時，比人話狂人<br />\n  睇黎狂人個果係金仔先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c425d4fd0f1d93ca70a794793d69cf1e629d45","tid":386400,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:53:00.000Z","msg":"金仔好尊重